text: “læa hak rea prasngkh læw nænxn rea k yk khea khun læa dwy brrda xongkar hela nan tæthwa khea khng man xyu kab din læa ptibati tam khwam khır fıta khxng khea dangnan xupma khxng phu nan cung dang xupmiy khxng sunakh hak cea khab li man man k ca hxb læb lin hxy lng nanhæla khux xupma klum chn thi ptiseth brrda xongkar khxng rea dangnan cea cng lea reuxngraw hela nan theid pheux wa phwk khea ca di khırkhrwy”
